         role="TOPIC">
  <title>Account Services</title>

  <section role="ITEM">
    <title>Account Services Introduction</title>

    <para role="TEXT">The Account Services Menu on the toolbar, provides
    facilities to manage company accounts and transactions through the
    <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml" xpointer="ent_appli"
    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/>.</para>

    <note role="TEXT">
      <para role="TEXT">The availability of the Account Services menu and its
      functions is dependent on the permissions assigned to the user. Only
      those functions the user is authorised to use, will be displayed.</para>
    </note>

    <para role="TEXT">This menu provides the following functions.</para>

    <para role="TEXT"><variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Balances and
          Transactions</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">process and sign existing transactions in the
            <xi:include href="../entities_en.xml" xpointer="ent_appli"
            xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/>.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Account
          Summary</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">Display a summary of transactions for accounts
            the user has authority to use.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Account
          Statement</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">Produce an on-screen or softcopy statement for
            an account the user has authority to use.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Account
          Details</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">View the details of accounts linked to the
            user.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Fees and
          Billing</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">View and pay fees and invoices sent by the
            bank.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Term deposit</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">Create and list Term Deposit accounts other than
            Certificate of Deposit for treasury accounts.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Position
          Management</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">Inquire about the previously executed
            transactions and Foreign Exchange positions related to an
            account.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>

        <varlistentry>
          <term><guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Regional Account
          View</guimenuitem></term>

          <listitem>
            <para role="TEXT">View the account balances of customers linked to
            your account profile. Customers can exist across different banks
            or branches and should be linked through a trust
            relationship.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
      </variablelist></para>

    <para role="TEXT"><note>
        <para role="TEXT">The term "account" is used in this section, to
        describe monetary accounts held at the bank. It is not used to
        describe User Login accounts.</para>
      </note></para>
  </section>

